race.comment: NORTHERN PRIDE (2) is in fine form and hasn't missed the frame in his past four starts. Last time out he scored over 1400m at Townsville. Racing very consistently of late and looks likely to keep the ball rolling. FLYING SHAMUS (7) turned in a modest performance when seventh last time out over 1200m at this circuit, beaten 5.5 lengths, after a win at this course at the previous outing. Nicely placed to feature in the finish. DIVINE OKAY (4) has a handy record here with a win and four placings from seven spins. In the mix. THE DRILLER (6) rounds out the selections in a race with only a handful of chances.
